summary: Now.. Imagine after a long night AND few days you are getting harrassed by your fans you work so hard for... Them banging on...
body:
Imagine being Harry Styles… A kind hearted and selfless person who performers every night.. Hardly has a break and has a smile on his face each time.

Now.. Imagine after a long night AND few days you are getting harrassed by your fans you work so hard for… Them banging on your car window and getting on top of the roof. Scared for not only their safety but your own… And THEN you wake up and find some fans from that SAME concert have been assaulted for getting a t shirt or a rainbow flag? 😭 😭

It’s a fcking mess! And it’s toxic.

GROW UP! Yall ain’t animals! You wasn’t raised in a zoo! This behavior is disgusting.

I love Harry like he is my child or even a friend. And seeing him go through that AND the inncont fans as well for the account of the NOT so innocent ones ain’t fair…im heartbroken. Sorry Harry…

Rant over.
